# AISBP ŌĆö GitHub push & VPS deploy

## Repository

- GitHub: `demodropai/aisbp` (`https://github.com/demodropai/aisbp.git`)
- Default branch: `main`
- Local machine: `gh` is usually logged in as **demodropai** with `repo` + `workflow` ŌĆö use `git push origin main` (no need to embed a PAT when gh credentials work).

## Auto-deploy (CI)

- Workflow: `.github/workflows/deploy-hostinger.yml` ŌĆö **Deploy Hostinger VPS**
- Triggers on push to `main` (and manual `workflow_dispatch`)
- Uses `hostinger/deploy-on-vps@v2` with VM id in GitHub var `HOSTINGER_VM_ID`
- This **initiates** a Hostinger Docker deploy but does **not** guarantee `/root/aisbp` on the VPS is updated for manual SSH builds.

## VPS

- Host: `72.62.243.54` (Hostinger VM `srv1267113` / id `1267113`)
- SSH user: `root`
- App path: `/root/aisbp`
- Production env: `/root/aisbp/.env.production`
- Compose file: `/root/aisbp/docker-compose.hostinger.yml`
- Public app: `https://kb.aisalesbot.pro` (Next on :3000 proxies to backend on :3001)
- Containers: `aisbp-backend-1`, `aisbp-frontend-1`, `aisbp-redis-1`

**Local credentials (gitignored):** `infra/vps/.deploy.local.env` ŌĆö copy from `.deploy.local.env.example`. Contains `GITHUB_PAT`, `SSH_HOST`, `SSH_USER`, `SSH_PASS`, `VPS_AISBP_PATH`. Never commit the real file.

For local `git push`, prefer `gh` auth when logged in as **demodropai**; use `GITHUB_PAT` from the deploy env file for VPS `git fetch` when needed.

## Manual backend deploy (SSH)

After push, if the VPS clone is stale or backend needs a forced rebuild:

```bash
cd /root/aisbp
git fetch origin main
git reset --hard origin/main
docker compose --env-file .env.production -f docker-compose.hostinger.yml build --no-cache backend
docker compose --env-file .env.production -f docker-compose.hostinger.yml up -d --force-recreate --no-deps backend
docker ps --filter name=backend
docker logs aisbp-backend-1 --tail 50
```

`git fetch` on the VPS: load `GITHUB_PAT` from `infra/vps/.deploy.local.env`, pull, then reset remote to `https://github.com/demodropai/aisbp.git` (no token left in URL).

## Verify deploy

- Backend up (via frontend proxy): `curl https://kb.aisalesbot.pro/api/v1/debug/runtime` ŌåÆ `401` without auth is OK; `502` means backend down.
- On VPS: `git log -1 --oneline` should match the pushed commit.

## Full-stack / frontend

To rebuild frontend after UI changes:

```bash
docker compose --env-file .env.production -f docker-compose.hostinger.yml build --no-cache frontend
docker compose --env-file .env.production -f docker-compose.hostinger.yml up -d --force-recreate --no-deps frontend
```

## Local helper (Windows)

Load `infra/vps/.deploy.local.env` for `SSH_PASS` / `GITHUB_PAT` when running SSH deploy scripts (e.g. under `.ssh-tmp/`, also gitignored).

